        "TileImage": "$($repository 7af86858-df9d-478b-b5d8-803379cd165f).Image",
        "Description": "Good day, 47. Your targets are Richard and Susan Wilson. They are hosting a party open for everyone. Intel sugests that after serving their hotdogs and burgers they plan to give out muffins from their neighbour, Helen West. As we know West mixes drugs and poison in her muffins, using them to experiment on people and the Wilsons are willingly helping her. I&apos;d say it&apos;s about time for the party to end.",
